286
00:19:44,933 --> 00:19:45,851
He's my friend.

287
00:19:46,852 --> 00:19:48,437
Members get discounts here, right?

288
00:19:49,563 --> 00:19:51,565
Yes, wait.

289
00:19:52,232 --> 00:19:53,066
Yeah.

290
00:19:54,735 --> 00:19:57,946
Here, put your name down
and your birthday and…

291
00:19:59,781 --> 00:20:03,660
Right, you get a free video
if you give them your pager number.

292
00:20:04,328 --> 00:20:05,621
Oh really?

293
00:20:19,968 --> 00:20:21,678
Hello, this is Baek Hyun-jin.

294
00:20:22,429 --> 00:20:25,682
Please let me hear your voice
after the beep.

295
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:37,819
I'm WBC's Na Bo-ra,
your host for Infinite Melodies.

296
00:20:37,903 --> 00:20:38,987
Hello, everyone.

297
00:20:39,446 --> 00:20:43,116
The Mushimcheon Cherry Blossom Festival
is said to start today.

298
00:20:43,909 --> 00:20:45,911
How about a trip after school

299
00:20:45,994 --> 00:20:49,331
to see the flowers at Musimcheon Stream?

300
00:21:13,897 --> 00:21:14,898
Did you eat yet?

301
00:21:14,982 --> 00:21:17,150
Let's eat together!

302
00:21:20,153 --> 00:21:22,197
Have a girlfriend?

303
00:21:22,906 --> 00:21:25,284
-No.
-How about an ideal type?

304
00:21:25,867 --> 00:21:26,702
I don't know…

305
00:21:28,453 --> 00:21:29,496
Shim Eun-ha?

306
00:21:32,791 --> 00:21:34,710
So, the pure, innocent type?

307
00:21:35,627 --> 00:21:36,545
That's perfect.

308
00:21:37,546 --> 00:21:38,714
Favorite movie?

309
00:21:40,299 --> 00:21:41,133
Armageddon.

310
00:21:41,717 --> 00:21:44,803
Huh? That's my favorite too. Armageddon.

311
00:21:45,804 --> 00:21:47,389
Desired college major?

312
00:21:49,182 --> 00:21:52,644
-Theater and Film or Mass Communication.
-Theater and Film…

313
00:21:52,728 --> 00:21:56,815
Planning to be a celebrity
with those good looks, huh?

314
00:21:58,525 --> 00:22:01,236
No, it's because
I like working with cameras.

315
00:22:03,447 --> 00:22:05,032
Likes to work with…

316
00:22:11,288 --> 00:22:13,332
Hey! I wasn't asking about you!

317
00:22:13,874 --> 00:22:15,625
I'm asking about Baek Hyun-jin!

318
00:22:16,293 --> 00:22:18,128
Ugh, I need to start over.

319
00:22:18,211 --> 00:22:21,965
Hey. Don't be lazy.
You should take some shots too.

320
00:22:22,966 --> 00:22:23,967
