You should know how to do this stuff.

322
00:22:30,223 --> 00:22:32,100
Well, how do you do it?

323
00:22:34,102 --> 00:22:34,936
Here.

324
00:22:36,313 --> 00:22:37,731
Put your eye right here.

325
00:22:40,525 --> 00:22:41,443
Your hand here.

326
00:22:44,988 --> 00:22:46,281
Use this to zoom in,

327
00:22:47,699 --> 00:22:48,784
this to zoom out.

328
00:22:50,577 --> 00:22:52,079
Oh, don't press too hard.

329
00:22:54,873 --> 00:22:55,707
You see it?

330
00:22:59,419 --> 00:23:02,547
Okay. I got it. You can go.

331
00:23:06,134 --> 00:23:07,135
Don't break it.

332
00:23:44,965 --> 00:23:47,050
-Wow.
-She's so fast!

333
00:23:47,759 --> 00:23:48,760
She's so good.

334
00:23:52,889 --> 00:23:56,351
Guys! There's a fight!
It's with the Paradise gang!

335
00:23:56,435 --> 00:23:58,186
-Really?
-Let's go watch!

336
00:23:59,729 --> 00:24:02,566
Hey, there's a fight. Let's go and watch.

337
00:24:03,150 --> 00:24:04,526
Did you hit on my girl?

338
00:24:05,193 --> 00:24:06,361
Come on, stop it!

339
00:24:06,445 --> 00:24:08,572
You can stay out of this, Bok-soon.

340
00:24:09,948 --> 00:24:12,951
You wouldn't have done that
if you knew who I am.

341
00:24:13,034 --> 00:24:15,829
I'm Min Hong-gi,
the Fire Fist of Cheongju.

342
00:24:15,912 --> 00:24:17,622
How dare you covet my girl.

343
00:24:17,706 --> 00:24:19,332
You're dead meat today.

344
00:24:19,416 --> 00:24:20,709
Damn it, seriously!

345
00:24:20,792 --> 00:24:24,921
I'm the one who had a crush on him!
He rejected me and it's mortifying enough.

346
00:24:26,756 --> 00:24:29,009
Bok-soon, I'm sorry.

347
00:24:29,759 --> 00:24:30,594
But…

348
00:24:32,429 --> 00:24:33,930
You shouldn't date this guy.

349
00:24:35,265 --> 00:24:36,808
Date a better man.

350
00:24:37,601 --> 00:24:38,435
Okay.

351
00:24:38,518 --> 00:24:39,853
What did you just say?

352
00:24:40,604 --> 00:24:42,439
Huh? That asshole…

353
00:24:42,522 --> 00:24:43,482
Hey.

354
00:24:50,614 --> 00:24:51,865
Who the hell was it?

355
00:24:51,948 --> 00:24:53,617
-Get that bastard!
-Huh?

356
00:24:59,247 --> 00:25:01,124
Run!

357
00:25:03,418 --> 00:25:05,170
Get out of my way! Get them!

358
00:25:11,343 --> 00:25:13,011
-Quick! Get them!
-Come here!

359
00:25:21,520 --> 00:25:23,230
-Damn it.
-Come here!

360
00:25:23,313 --> 00:25:25,315
-What? Why?
-The cops are there.

361
00:25:25,398 --> 00:25:26,733
Sir, please get in the car.

362
00:25:27,734 --> 00:25:29,152
All right, then. See you later.

363
00:25:29,819 --> 00:25:31,321
Look, he's smiling.

364
00:25:33,156 --> 00:25:35,242
Just ask that person over there.

365
00:25:35,325 --> 00:25:37,035
-It wasn't me!
-My goodness.

366
00:25:37,118 --> 00:25:38,745
I did nothing wrong.

367
00:25:39,496 --> 00:25:41,206
What did I do, huh?

368
00:25:45,418 --> 00:25:46,878
Are you insane?

369
00:25:46,962 --> 00:25:49,047
That guy is in Paradise.

370
00:25:49,130 --> 00:25:51,633
Be careful.
You'll get killed at this rate!

371
00:25:53,593 --> 00:25:54,678
Are you all right?

372
00:26:22,163 --> 00:26:22,998
Are you okay?

373
00:26:24,291 --> 00:26:26,876
I had you learn taekwondo
so you could protect yourself.

374
00:26:26,960 --> 00:26:29,713
But here you are,
getting into fights with guys.

375
00:26:29,796 --> 00:26:31,881
Who'd fall for you like that?

376
00:26:32,674 --> 00:26:34,676
There are lots of guys
who want to date me.

377
00:26:34,759 --> 00:26:36,428
Whatever.

378
00:26:36,511 --> 00:26:39,472
Anyway, when you get home,
don't say you got hurt fighting.

379
00:26:39,556 --> 00:26:41,182
Your mother will worry.

380
00:26:41,266 --> 00:26:42,934
You know she gets scared easily.

381
00:26:43,018 --> 00:26:45,895
I wish all guys were like you, Dad.

382
00:26:48,857 --> 00:26:51,568
I guess you have
a good eye for men. Goodness.

383
00:26:53,778 --> 00:26:55,363
It was really humid yesterday.

384
00:26:55,864 --> 00:26:58,074
Hey! You know
the new internet cafe nearby?

385
00:26:58,158 --> 00:27:01,411
I heard the guy who works there
is super hot. Let's go see him!

386
00:27:01,494 --> 00:27:03,705
Leave me out.
I'm going to the broadcasting club.

387
00:27:03,788 --> 00:27:05,290
-Huh?
-Just go with us.

388
00:27:05,373 --> 00:27:07,584
No, go without me.
I only waited to say bye.

389
00:27:07,667 --> 00:27:08,835
-Bye.
-Just take a look.

390
00:27:22,682 --> 00:27:24,142
Na Bo-ra, hop on.

391
00:27:26,811 --> 00:27:29,064
-Wow! Go!
-Hey, he wants you to get on.

392
00:27:29,147 --> 00:27:30,815
-Go, come on.
-Why me?

393
00:27:34,027 --> 00:27:37,197
Hey, where are you going?
You need to turn right.

394
00:27:37,280 --> 00:27:39,199
I don't know how to turn right.

395
00:27:39,282 --> 00:27:40,116
What?

396
00:27:41,117 --> 00:27:44,871
You-- Where are we going? Make a U-turn!

397
00:27:44,954 --> 00:27:48,041
-I don't know how to do that, either.
-What?

398
00:27:48,625 --> 00:27:49,459
Hey!

399
00:27:50,126 --> 00:27:52,253
How can you drive like that?

400
00:27:53,171 --> 00:27:55,799
Sorry, I'm still learning.

401
00:27:57,509 --> 00:28:00,929
I borrowed it from a guy I know,
just so I could give you a ride.

402
00:28:04,015 --> 00:28:05,058
Me? Why?

403
00:28:08,770 --> 00:28:10,605
You got hurt because of me.

404
00:28:17,404 --> 00:28:18,697
Why'd you do that?

405
00:28:19,948 --> 00:28:20,782
Uh…

406
00:28:22,033 --> 00:28:25,161
Because if you got hurt,
someone would be really sad.

407
00:28:25,245 --> 00:28:26,663
Were you worried about me?

408
00:28:30,709 --> 00:28:35,338
It looked like you'd get beaten to death.
Was I supposed to just let it happen?

409
00:28:37,257 --> 00:28:40,885
Also, you shouldn't smile and be nice
to just anybody.

410
00:28:41,594 --> 00:28:43,388
Your friends will be annoyed.

411
00:28:45,890 --> 00:28:48,476
-Are you asking me out?
-Huh?

412
00:28:50,019 --> 00:28:53,690
What? Me? Asking out? Who?

413
00:28:56,860 --> 00:29:00,780
Cut the nonsense and take me back.
I need to go to the broadcasting room.

414
00:29:05,577 --> 00:29:06,578
Fine.

415
00:29:07,579 --> 00:29:08,413
Get on.

416
00:29:13,084 --> 00:29:13,918
Huh?

417
00:29:18,465 --> 00:29:19,674
It's not starting.

418
00:29:20,633 --> 00:29:21,468
What?

419
00:29:22,969 --> 00:29:25,138
-Hey!
-Wait, hey.

420
00:29:26,723 --> 00:29:28,016
I can do it.

421
00:29:28,099 --> 00:29:30,018
This isn't that hard.

422
00:29:41,863 --> 00:29:43,072
Let's just go eat.

423
00:29:57,212 --> 00:29:59,464
When did you get here, Poong Woon-ho?

424
00:29:59,547 --> 00:30:00,590
A moment ago.

425
00:30:03,843 --> 00:30:05,762
I'll wash my hands. Take a seat.

426
00:30:12,602 --> 00:30:14,229
Did you wait for me?

427
00:30:15,188 --> 00:30:16,022
Sorry.

428
00:30:34,541 --> 00:30:35,375
Let's date.

429
00:30:39,045 --> 00:30:40,213
Huh?

430
00:30:43,258 --> 00:30:44,092
I like you.

431
00:30:49,597 --> 00:30:51,683
Here, drink this.

432
00:30:57,814 --> 00:30:58,731
You like

433
00:30:59,732 --> 00:31:00,567
me?

434
00:31:00,650 --> 00:31:01,651
Yeah.

435
00:31:01,734 --> 00:31:02,652
Why?

436
00:31:02,735 --> 00:31:05,154
You can't like me! This isn't right.

437
00:31:06,739 --> 00:31:10,368
Hey, I can eat two whole pizzas.
Can you handle that?

438
00:31:10,451 --> 00:31:12,996
Even now, I really want
to steal your food.

439
00:31:13,079 --> 00:31:15,665
Just look at this. I can eat so much food.

440
00:31:21,421 --> 00:31:22,630
That's good.

441
00:31:24,674 --> 00:31:28,094
There's a pizza shop across the street
that my father owns too.

442
00:31:30,388 --> 00:31:31,514
Really?

443
00:31:31,598 --> 00:31:32,807
Yeah.

444
00:31:32,891 --> 00:31:34,225
I rarely take showers.

445
00:31:35,184 --> 00:31:36,936
See this? See how oily it is?

446
00:31:37,020 --> 00:31:40,064
I haven't washed my hair in two days.
I also have tons of dandruff.

447
00:31:40,148 --> 00:31:43,234
I'm a terrible student,
mark the third answer on math tests,

448
00:31:43,318 --> 00:31:44,652
and have a nasty temper too.

449
00:31:44,736 --> 00:31:47,113
My dad says he feels bad
for my future boyfriend.

450
00:31:47,196 --> 00:31:48,823
And I…

451
00:31:50,325 --> 00:31:53,077
I can even fart to children's songs!

452
00:31:58,833 --> 00:31:59,667
Sorry.

453
00:32:00,793 --> 00:32:02,045
I need to go.

454
00:32:42,001 --> 00:32:42,835
What is this?

455
00:32:43,836 --> 00:32:44,921
It's about to blow!

456
00:33:31,134 --> 00:33:34,679
I thought you had a crush on Hyun-jin.

457
00:33:36,597 --> 00:33:37,515
I don't.

458
00:33:38,891 --> 00:33:41,227
I'm just interested in him.

459
00:33:42,895 --> 00:33:44,439
Isn't that the same thing?

460
00:33:44,981 --> 00:33:46,524
It's totally different.

461
00:33:47,025 --> 00:33:48,568
Interest is just interest.

462
00:33:50,236 --> 00:33:51,571
And liking someone is…

463
00:33:56,743 --> 00:33:58,161
Liking someone is?

464
00:34:05,376 --> 00:34:06,377
