465
00:34:07,628 --> 00:34:08,629
Try standing up.

466
00:34:17,346 --> 00:34:20,224
If you sprain your ankle once,
it's easy to sprain it again.

467
00:34:20,308 --> 00:34:21,893
Next time, use your fists.

468
00:34:24,395 --> 00:34:25,229
Bye.

469
00:34:33,446 --> 00:34:34,280
Yeon-doo.

470
00:34:35,698 --> 00:34:38,367
I think my heart is acting
a bit weird too.

471
00:34:40,203 --> 00:34:42,330
YEON-DOO, A LOT HAPPENED
OVER THE PAST FEW DAYS.

472
00:34:42,413 --> 00:34:44,332
ACTUALLY… I THINK HYUN-JIN LIKES M--

473
