BAEK HYUN-JIN IS A PLAYBOY.

474
00:34:50,171 --> 00:34:52,548
ABOUT THAT GUY, POONG WOON-HO…

475
00:34:53,841 --> 00:34:56,886
Never mind. I can take care of it.

476
00:35:00,515 --> 00:35:01,599
Is it good now?

477
00:35:02,100 --> 00:35:03,142
One, two…

478
00:35:06,604 --> 00:35:08,773
Guys, don't crumple your faces like that.

479
00:35:08,856 --> 00:35:10,108
All right, smile.

480
00:35:10,191 --> 00:35:12,735
You with the messy hair!
Your hair's blocking the others.

481
00:35:12,819 --> 00:35:15,863
Look at the people next to you.
Bend down a bit more, okay.

482
00:35:15,947 --> 00:35:18,241
One, two, three…

483
00:35:18,324 --> 00:35:20,034
means I'll take the picture.

484
00:35:21,869 --> 00:35:26,374
This is mulberry extract.
It's what Gyeongju is known for.

485
00:35:26,457 --> 00:35:29,585
It's great for chronic fatigue,
hypertension, cancer, dementia,

486
00:35:29,669 --> 00:35:31,379
and even your heart.

487
00:35:31,462 --> 00:35:33,631
It's the best gift for your parents.

488
00:35:33,714 --> 00:35:35,299
Hey, wait here. Okay?

489
00:35:37,468 --> 00:35:39,679
-How much for one of these, sir?
-30,000 won.

490
00:35:40,304 --> 00:35:41,722
Here's 20,000 won.

491
00:35:43,683 --> 00:35:45,893
Please take this, sir. Just a second.

492
00:35:46,727 --> 00:35:48,688
-Do you have 3,000--
-Here you go, sir.

493
00:35:52,608 --> 00:35:53,442
What?

494
00:35:56,654 --> 00:35:58,322
You really are something else.

495
00:35:59,365 --> 00:36:03,161
By the way, when we start dating,
will you let me hear you fart to songs?

496
00:36:05,580 --> 00:36:06,706
Follow me!

497
00:36:07,206 --> 00:36:08,040
Hey…

498
00:36:10,168 --> 00:36:13,462
Are you insane? How could you say that
in front of all those people?

499
00:36:16,465 --> 00:36:18,050
1010235.

500
00:36:18,134 --> 00:36:19,051
What?

501
00:36:19,135 --> 00:36:21,345
You said you love me passionately.

502
00:36:21,429 --> 00:36:23,598
Only my family and Woon-ho
know my pager number.

503
00:36:23,681 --> 00:36:25,683
And you. Bora Video.

504
00:36:27,810 --> 00:36:31,230
Ugh! I love you passionately?

505
00:36:31,314 --> 00:36:35,735
